{"tid":1004573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞典飯店免費住宿  條件是完全不能用手機","createTime":"2019-02-01T14:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T18:35:27.000Z","uid":32511,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c7ad03e84054ccc3dad5021e21e9ed64986548","tid":1004573,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"現在很多飯店都有提供WiFi，讓遊客住房也能用手機上網。不過瑞典一間飯店最近為了鼓勵大家不要划手機，就推出一種特別的客房，房價將依房客使用手機時間的量收費，如果完全不用手機，就能免費入住。<br />\n<br />\n綜合報導指出，瑞典貝羅拉酒店（Hotel Bellora）最近推出一種特別的住房計畫，這種客房內會擺放一種可以偵測液晶螢幕使用量的高科技檯燈，如果顧客在住房期間沒有使用手機，房價就是0元。但顧客每使用手機1分鐘，房價就會增加20元瑞典克朗（約68元新台幣），如果總使用時間超過30分鐘，就需要支付全額的房價。<br />\n<br />\n貝羅拉酒店希望透過這樣的住房計畫，讓大家少花時間在上網、多花時間在現實生活中與人互動。其實除了網路以外，飯店也設有屋頂露天酒吧、世紀中期現代主義（MidCentury Modern）風格的義大利餐廳，讓顧客可以體驗手機外的娛樂。"},{"pid":"57708eb4cc1607d7b4f9979255064a73bb55d672","tid":1004573,"uid":1713,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"唔用手機 用pad lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36ca20ddac70460972a66a58fc82c059eeeb8d7","tid":1004573,"uid":231583,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"57708eb4cc1607d7b4f9979255064a73bb55d672","tid":1004573,"uid":1713,"like":1,"dislike":30,"score":-29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:14:58.000Z","msg":"唔用手機 用pad lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:33:11.000Z","msg":"好威比你搵到漏洞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f